        (84517, 'Taylor Dooley', '1993-02-26', 'Success has arrived early for Taylor Dooley. She can next be seen in The Adventures of Sharkboy and Lavagirl 3-D (2005) (opens June 10) from director ''Robert Rodriquez (I)'' (Spy Kids (2001)). Taylor will portray "Lava Girl", who comes to life as an imaginary friend to a lonely 10-year-old boy.

