In her free time, Taylor is a very active 12-year-old. She enjoys horseback riding, dancing and swimming. She currently resides in Los Angeles with her parents and younger brother.', 'Michigan, USA', 1, '/dmCRmKnwx25jOgI3WXIYzisI4YC.jpg'),
