        (88519, 'Evan Richards', '1975-03-25', 'Actor, filmmaker / producer. 

As an actor Evan has starred or co-starred in various film and television projects including "Down and Out in Beverly Hills" and the television series of "Bill and Ted''s Excellent Adventures". As a filmmaker, Evan''s short film "Woman X" was shortlisted for a BAFTA award and was shown on HBO and Starz. His other short film "Cloud Nine" was a Skky Vodka Short Film Festival finalist and was seen on HBO. His debut feature film "In a Day" played numerous festivals and won various awards. After a theatrical run in Los Angeles, "In a Day" was picked up for distribution by IFC Films. It was also sold to territories worldwide.

