        (89455, 'Tommy Lee', '1962-10-03', 'Thomas Lee Bass (born October 3, 1962) is an American musician and founding member of Mötley Crüe. As well as being the band''s long-term drummer, Lee founded rap-metal band Methods of Mayhem, and has pursued solo musical projects.

