He made his first appearance on the stage in Toronto, Ontario, Canada in 1887 and worked continuously after that date including prominent parts on the New York stage as well as in films. He also wrote and produced plays.', 'London, England, U.K.', 1, '/az4OS4Ulj08n54LyP5xvswWZfMT.jpg'),
