        (96349, 'Molly C. Quinn', '1993-10-08', 'Molly C. Quinn (born October 8, 1993, height 5'' 5" (1,65 m)) is an American actress whose works have included theatre, film, and television. Since March 2009, she has played Alexis Castle, the main character''s daughter, in ABC''s Castle.

