        (109870, 'Tom Woodruff Jr.', '1959-01-01', 'Tom Woodruff Jr.is an American special effects artist and actor who portrayed the Lead Alien in the 1997 film Alien Resurrection and ''Grid'' in the 2004 film Alien vs. Predator. 

