        (110990, 'Tamara Jolaine', '1983-05-20', 'Tamara Jolaine, began her acting career in Canada. At age 18, around the time of her completion of her Political Science degree at the University of Toronto, she cast aside her plans to attend law school and began an artistic journey revolving around both acting and music.  In Toronto, Tamara worked on many film and commercial projects. The feature independent film

